title: Internet Download Manager IDM 6.25 Build 14 + Patch
description:
What's new in version 6.25 Build 14

(Released: Mar 11, 2016)

Added support for Firefox 46

How to Install: ( Note: Please strictly follow the installation guide to avoid errors)

1. Install idm by running "idman625build14.exe"

Note: no need to exit / close idm if running.

2. Run "32bit Patch build 14.exe" if you're using 32bit operating system
or
Run "64bit Patch build 14.exe" if you're using 64bit operating system

3. Done. Enjoy simplest IDM installation ever

To uninstall this patch see text file added inside this torrent, please.

This torrent is tested and safe to install but if your antivirus give any type of error so don't worry just disable your antivirus and install.
It'll not harm your computer or anything because it's 100% tested and safe
